<p><span>▲厦门援建的临夏吉明鞋业东西协作扶贫车间。</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200918/e228f17762d0493b94b7471affd4f86d.gif" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
